java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.analysis.multi.MultiAnalysis<LState,RState,DataState,LControl,RControl,LAction,RAction,LPrec,RPrec,DataPrec,LControlPrec,RControlPrec,MState,MBlankState,MAction>
Type Parameters:
LState - Type of combined (with data) state of left formalism
RState - Type of combined (with data) state of right formalism
DataState - Type of data state
LControl - Type of control state from left formalism
RControl - Type of control state from right formalism
LAction - Type of action from left formalism
RAction - Type of action from right formalism
LPrec - Type of precision of left formalism
RPrec - Type of precision of right formalism
DataPrec - Type of data precision (formalism independent)
